Overview Notes: Suboptimal vitamin D levels - consider supplementing with vitamin D (5000iu daily) and recheck your levels after 3 months
Comment Key: ClinicalExamComment
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Clinical Recommendations: -Audiology report is congruent with the know hearing loss in the left ear. Use of your hearing devise will improve your hearing in the affected ear.
Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Continue to monitor your BP and cholesterol levels, try to lose some weight, exercise regularly and eat a healthy diet.
Comment Key: ClinicalExamComment
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Continue to monitor your BP and cholesterol levels, try to lose some weight, exercise regularly and eat a healthy diet.

Comment Key: CurrentComplaintRecommendation
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Overview Notes: Above optimal homocysteine levels - consider supplementing with active B vitamins such as those in phytomulti by metagenics
Comment Key: EyesightNote
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Comment Value: All bloods within normal. Cholesterol well controlled, suboptimal vitamin D and above optimal homocysteine. Borderline uric acid
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Nurse: Lebo Cindi
Clinical Recommendations: -Audiology report is congruent with the know hearing loss in the left ear. Use of your hearing devise will improve your hearing in the affected ear.
Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Suboptimal vitamin D levels - consider supplementing with vitamin D (5000iu daily) and recheck your levels after 3 months
Comment Key: LifestyleNote
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Overview Notes: Suboptimal vitamin D levels; Above optimal homocysteine levels; Borderline uric acid level
Hypertension and hyperlipidaemia - but both well controlled; abnormal hearing screen
Comment Key: MedicalHistoryRecommendation
Comment Value: -You are managing the hypertension and cholesterol well. Continue with the lifestyle changes you have made.
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Overview Notes: Above optimal homocysteine levels - consider supplementing with active B vitamins such as those in phytomulti by metagenics
Comment Key: MensHealthNote
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Above optimal homocysteine levels - consider supplementing with active B vitamins such as those in phytomulti by metagenics
Comment Key: MentalHealthAnxietyRecommendation
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Clinical Recommendations: -Audiology report is congruent with the know hearing loss in the left ear. Use of your hearing devise will improve your hearing in the affected ear.
Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Nil

Clinical Recommendations: -Audiology report is congruent with the know hearing loss in the left ear. Use of your hearing devise will improve your hearing in the affected ear.
Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Suboptimal vitamin D levels - consider supplementing with vitamin D (5000iu daily) and recheck your levels after 3 months
Comment Key: MentalHealthNote
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Clinical Recommendations: -Audiology report is congruent with the know hearing loss in the left ear. Use of your hearing devise will improve your hearing in the affected ear.
Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Suboptimal vitamin D levels - consider supplementing with vitamin D (5000iu daily) and recheck your levels after 3 months
Comment Key: MentalHealthStressRecommendation
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Nurse: Lebo Cindi
Clinical Recommendations: 
Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations:

assist with subsequent management. Will likely require ENT referral

Overview Notes: Continue to monitor your BP and cholesterol levels, try to lose some weight, exercise regularly and eat a healthy diet.
Comment Key: SpecialInvestigationNote
Comment Value: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Non smoker; Meat free diet during the week
Fair amount of exercise
Comment Key: SpecialInvestigationRecommendation
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Overview Notes: Borderline uric acid level - you are already making sure that you don't eat too much red meat but try to reduce your alcohol consumption and make sure that you are drinking enough water
Comment Key: SymptomScreeningNote
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Fair amount of risk factors
Comment Key: VitalsNote
Comment Value: High BMI 
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Clinical Recommendations: -Audiology report is congruent with the know hearing loss in the left ear. Use of your hearing devise will improve your hearing in the affected ear.
Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations: 
Overview Notes: Suboptimal vitamin D levels; Above optimal homocysteine levels; Borderline uric acid level
Hypertension and hyperlipidaemia - but both well controlled; abnormal hearing screen
Comment Key: VitaminsOrSupplements
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Lung function slightly abnormal due to rib fracture (Decreased PEF)

Men's Health Recommendations: -Prostate specific antigen is within normal limits. If the changes to your urinary habits persist please see a urologist.
Women's Health Recommendations:
